      "description": "## Attested releases\n\nRelease assets are now built from source in GitHub Actions and ship with signed [artifact attestations](https://docs.github.com/en/actions/how-tos/secure-your-work/use-artifact-attestations/use-artifact-attestations) (SLSA build provenance). Starting with this release, verify any downloaded asset with:\n\n```bash\ngh attestation verify main.js --repo 2easy/nudge\n```\n\nNo plugin functionality changes since 0.5.0.\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/2easy/nudge/compare/0.5.0...0.5.1\n",
